data.description: As you enter the lovely tree lined street of the beautiful Southern Hills Plantation Golf & Country Club you notice the rolling hills and very laid back lifestyle that awaits. Located in the 55 plus gated part of the Cascades at Southern Hills this 1704 square foot 2 bedroom, 2 bath, with office/den built in 2020 with over 20k in upgrades. Some of the features of this home include bull nose corners, 5 1/4 inch upgraded baseboards throughout, waterproof faux wood vinyl flooring, spacious foyer entrance with new front storm door, upgraded deep kitchen sink, mud room, ethernet cable in all rooms, top of the line Aquasana Water Purification System, floor outlets in family/living room, glass window/screened spacious lanai, faux custom blinds throughout, large corner lot with greenspace behind it & built in home team pest defense system. The gourmet kitchen is appointed with rich espresso wood cabinets and quartz countertops with a stunning center island breakfast bar perfect for entertaining, stainless steel appliances, pantry, upgraded lighting and ceiling fans, soft closing cabinets & drawers, gas line hookup included if you want to change range, w/d or hot water heater from electric to gas. Open floor plan with huge family/living room and dining room. Master Suite has carpet and large walk in closet. Master Bath is appointed with spacious double sink, Corian vanity with plenty of cabinet storage space also with soft closing cabinets & drawers, seamless glass shower with bench seating and built-in grab bars, upgraded mosaic tiles & a separate closet and linen cabinet.  Split floor plan with large 2nd bedroom and guest bath that is tastefully finished with Corian countertops vanity and tile tub/shower combo. Inside laundry hookup with plenty of storage and nook area for all of your extras. When sitting on your front porch you have a partial pond view to watch all the nature in the community. Home is also considered a Smart Home ready for your Alexa and Guardian set up for keyless front door and cell phone controlled air/heat, double pane windows. Community features gated security, clubhouse with pool and outdoor recreational fun! Also Included in your HOA fee is cable and internet, lawn care and irrigation. Right outside your front door You are also on the threshold of 1 of the Best Golf Courses in the county. Memberships are available to residents of the Cascades.
